@BeerGameAPI_HostAddress = http://localhost:5219

### Health check
GET {{BeerGameAPI_HostAddress}}/api/healthz
Accept: application/json

### Get game state
GET {{BeerGameAPI_HostAddress}}/api/game/state
Accept: application/json

### Reset game
POST {{BeerGameAPI_HostAddress}}/api/game/reset
Accept: application/json

### Get player state
GET {{BeerGameAPI_HostAddress}}/api/game/players/retailer
Accept: application/json

### Get current turn
GET {{BeerGameAPI_HostAddress}}/api/turns/current
Accept: application/json

### Process arrivals
POST {{BeerGameAPI_HostAddress}}/api/turns/process-arrivals?role=retailer
Accept: application/json

### Advance turn
POST {{BeerGameAPI_HostAddress}}/api/turns/advance
Accept: application/json

### Place order
POST {{BeerGameAPI_HostAddress}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromRole": "retailer",
  "quantity": 4
}

### List orders
GET {{BeerGameAPI_HostAddress}}/api/orders
Accept: application/json

### Fulfill order
POST {{BeerGameAPI_HostAddress}}/api/orders/1/fulfill
Accept: application/json

### List events
GET {{BeerGameAPI_HostAddress}}/api/events
Accept: application/json

### Acknowledge event
POST {{BeerGameAPI_HostAddress}}/api/events/1/acknowledge
Accept: application/json

### Analytics summary
GET {{BeerGameAPI_HostAddress}}/api/analytics/summary
Accept: application/json

### Analytics history
GET {{BeerGameAPI_HostAddress}}/api/analytics/history
Accept: application/json

### Transit queue
GET {{BeerGameAPI_HostAddress}}/api/analytics/transit
Accept: application/json
